### 1.1 ROOT HTML/BODY CONFIGURATION

The `<html>` element must have `scroll-behavior: smooth` applied globally. The `<body>` element must be configured with:
- `background-color: var(--color-bg-base)` — pure `#000000`
- `color: var(--color-text-secondary)` — `#A1A1AA` as default body text
- `font-family: var(--font-body)`
